OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Amazon has pledged to hire 5,000       
OL,6, Ukrainian and other refugees in Europe 
OL,7, as part of a wider drive to help people
OL,8, fleeing persecution.                   
OL,10,FHilton Hotels, Adecco and Microsoft are
OL,11,Falso among the firms promising to offer
OL,12,Fwork or career support.                
OL,14,FIt comes as the global number of people
OL,15,Fforcibly displaced from their countries
OL,16,Fstands at a record 110 million.        
OL,18,FMargaritis Schinas, Vice-President of  
OL,19,Fthe European Commission, said far too  
OL,20,Fmany refugees could not find work.     
